<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Security Alert: Backup Code Used</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .alert-header {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .details-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-title {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .details-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .details-list li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .action-section {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .action-section h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .action-section ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .action-section li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {{#if companyLogo}}
            <img src="{{companyLogo}}" alt="{{companyName}}" class="logo">
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="alert-header">⚠️ Security Alert</h2>
            
            <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>We detected that a backup code was used to access your {{companyName}} account.</p>
            
            <div class="details-box">
                <h3 class="details-title">Account Access Details:</h3>
                <ul class="details-list">
                    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{currentTime}}</li>
                    <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Method:</strong> Backup Code</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-section">
                <h3>If this was you:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>No action is required</li>
                    <li>Consider regenerating your backup codes for enhanced security</li>
                    <li>Review your authenticator devices</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-section">
                <h3>If this wasn't you:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Change your password immediately</li>
                    <li>Disable and re-enable 2FA</li>
                    <li>Generate new backup codes</li>
                    <li>Contact support if needed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>For your security, the used backup code has been invalidated and can no longer be used.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The {{companyName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated security notification from {{companyName}}.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
            {{#if unsubscribeLink}}
            <p><a href="{{unsubscribeLink}}">Unsubscribe</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 